1
00:00:00,570 --> 00:00:04,900
[Fated Hearts – Suige's Fitness Results Revealed]

2
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:09,640
[On-set of "Fated Hearts"] [Working out during breaks]

3
00:00:09,810 --> 00:00:14,430
[Arm strength training]

4
00:00:14,570 --> 00:00:18,050
[A wide variety of workouts]

5
00:00:27,020 --> 00:00:28,320
[Dripping with sweat]

6
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,870
[Drenched in sweat] [Checking training stats]

7
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:33,110
[Satisfied]

8
00:00:33,140 --> 00:00:33,900
What kind of partnership?

9
00:00:33,180 --> 00:00:38,210
[Running lines]

10
00:00:33,900 --> 00:00:36,500
Looks to me like you're trying to humiliate me.

11
00:00:37,140 --> 00:00:38,140
Push him away.

12
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:39,700
[And down she goes—gracefully and dramatically]

13
00:00:40,730 --> 00:00:41,600
It wasn't me!

14
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:42,600
It wasn't me!

15
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:43,700
[Frantically proving innocence]

16
00:00:42,740 --> 00:00:43,940
That wasn't me!

17
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:46,040
I'm being framed!

18
00:00:44,820 --> 00:00:45,830
[Pure survival instinct]

19
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:46,960
Oh my god—

20
00:00:46,990 --> 00:00:47,610
Slow down!

21
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:50,180
[Fails to get up]

22
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:50,930
Touch it.

23
00:00:50,930 --> 00:00:51,790
Go on, touch it.

24
00:00:52,140 --> 00:00:53,380
[Tentative poke]

25
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:55,530
Qin,

26
00:00:55,530 --> 00:00:57,730
what do you think of Zheyuan's muscles?

27
00:00:58,820 --> 00:01:00,380
I thought they were fake just now.

28
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:00,980
[Bursts out laughing]

29
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,130
Now Zheyuan's upset.

30
00:01:03,130 --> 00:01:04,400
He's worked hard for years,

31
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:06,060
sticking to his fitness meals.

32
00:01:06,060 --> 00:01:07,900
So basically, you're complimenting me in disguise.

33
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:08,960
Actually, that makes me pretty happy.

34
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:10,260
They look unreal though!

35
00:01:10,260 --> 00:01:11,410
Oh my god.

36
00:01:10,470 --> 00:01:11,320
[Thumbs up for you]

37
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,170
We should add a bathing scene.

38
00:01:11,510 --> 00:01:13,230
[Making a wish]

39
00:01:13,190 --> 00:01:15,190
Let him show off properly.

40
00:01:15,390 --> 00:01:15,990
We've got one, we've got one!

41
00:01:15,990 --> 00:01:17,130
Bathing—

42
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:18,840
and wiping—

43
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:19,960
getting a little scrape.

44
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:20,450
That could work.

45
00:01:20,450 --> 00:01:21,100
That could definitely work.

46
00:01:21,100 --> 00:01:22,530
You've got to see it for yourself.

47
00:01:22,530 --> 00:01:24,070
[Stay tuned!]
